<s> Hi Terry, There are some XML variants: .xsl  </s>
<s> XSL Stylesheet .xslt  </s>
<s> XSL Transform .xsd  </s>
<s> XML Schema I am sure there are others.  </s>
<s> Although, I might avoid generic XML by default.  </s>
<s> As you know, Tidy isn't 100% whitespace safe for those XML variants that demand it.  </s>
<s> I handle this problem by keeping different types of files in separate directories.  </s>
<s> E.g. I don't mix executables and markup files.  </s>
<s> Also, I use consistent files extensions on markup files: either .xml/.xsl/.xsd or .html.  </s>
<s> I bulk Tidy only .html files.  </s>
<s> Sometimes I tidy XML files for readability, but I usually throw away the result for the reason above.  </s>
<s> hth, Charlie  </s>
